| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-5765 — Recovery Inhibition (lockbit3)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 184a5aa4-17d2-510b-8ab0-56f3f3ca1f65"
